{"tid":230162,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企成日都有人打黎白撞？","createTime":"2017-05-05T07:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:01:05.000Z","uid":89034,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b197afd38829fa584d01a7fea319e32405e21d1","tid":230162,"uid":89034,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"屋企個電話成日都有條友打黎白撞<br />\n由我初中到宜家讀u，差唔多隔一個月就打黎一次<br />\n多數一打黎就問我係咪_ _ _ ？（中文名但次次都唔同）<br />\n但事實上屋企無呢個人係度<br />\n初中果陣試過玩鳩佢，扮相認又試過，唱歌同講粗口比佢聽又試過，直接問佢係咪借錢都試過，但佢依舊間唔中都打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到今日兩點幾，屋企個電話又響，又係無來電顯示<br />\n琴晚天光先訓，本身比個電話嘈醒已經好撚燥，一接個電話又係佢打黎白撞<br />\n我即刻話：「咪撚嘈住我訓覺啊，屌你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」跟住就收左佢線<br />\n過左幾秒佢又即刻打黎，今次我無出聲，等佢出聲先，今次佢竟然話：「我就係要打黎呀，咁點丫？」<br />\n嘩屌你老母今次真係火都黎，我嬲撚到一野將部電話dum撚左落地，再抆撚曬d電話線，跟住再訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔係想問邊度整moon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係想問有無得叫電訊公司block左呢個電話，同埋查下呢條友咩料，唔知無來電顯示check唔check到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d233d0b1f7b81a2956ae90e112e85cdd52f2cf42","tid":230162,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c92f628c9c46cb40e87ca2f8748a269051eefbad","tid":230162,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"其實可以報警"},{"pid":"c4e41362260198afb296acedb6dd40e4ef18bcc9","tid":230162,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n過左幾秒佢又即刻打黎，今次我無出聲，等佢出聲先，今次佢竟然話：「我就係要打黎呀，咁點丫？」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e48e52e902c885cd2dc10bd949ed9a611a80ed","tid":230162,"uid":89034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好有錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf4a1f331fbd59cbd6aaecd34ef8d1d501a127c","tid":230162,"uid":89034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以報警</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢再打黎我就真係會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98801e724bb556da544c4b3146462c93e57111d","tid":230162,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"無來電就俾少少錢申請拒接停示者功能啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報警肯落案或者有人同你查既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a572e4daf76c429365ab9de0917e9279bebe40bf","tid":230162,"uid":22696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"有功能係block無來電 要俾錢"},{"pid":"6228151960d0546a904797b6f77ccf07363a0927","tid":230162,"uid":64208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:16:41.000Z","msg":"你以其人之道還治其人之身，佢一打黎就鳩叫or淨重覆佢講嘅野，鬥痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4046a331b64233a005db89d8ea65625cee84117","tid":230162,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你以其人之道還治其人之身，佢一打黎就鳩叫or淨重覆佢講嘅野，鬥痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打你咁撚癲, 你係唔係仲係青山未出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d60a947c85463acb0ea7a387fce1fff39584d3d","tid":230162,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4f62910e06778